summary: This will add some trees and other small things to make Riverwood look better
descriptionHtml:
I was a little bit disappointed with the vanilla Riverwood.
I added more plants, trees and other details to make Riverwood look more beautiful.



Installation:

Just drop the Forested Riverwood.esp into your Data folder

Uninstallation:

Just delete the Forested Riverwood.esp



This mod may conflict with any other mod that edits Riverwood


| Please report any bugs if you find some |
author: BlackWolf25
